reviewText: This gift lit up a Gandchilds eyes to the max!
This is one of my oldest kids favorite shows.
I really enjoy watching Sagwa.  Wish the other DVD's were available,  for a reasonable price.  Cannot believe Sagwa is so difficult to find.
I ordered this for my recently adopted daughter from China.  She loved it! It was recommended to me by my good friend and I'm very glad I bought it.  Very fast shipping as well. Thank you!
